MISCELLANEOUS DISMISSALS

2002- 0921. Lawyers Title Ins. Corp. v. Midwest Title Agency, Inc.

Delaware App. Nos. 01CAE10046 and 01CAE11059, 2002-0hio-2511. This cause is pending before the court as an appeal from the Court of Appeals for Delaware County. Upon consideration of appellant’s application for dismissal,

IT IS ORDERED by the court that the application for dismissal be, and hereby is, granted.

ACCORDINGLY, IT IS FURTHER ORDERED by the court that this cause be, and hereby is, dismissed.
